<i>[Episode 04]</i>

13
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:03,340
He comes to enjoy flowers at midnight.

14
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,400
Interesting.

15
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,160
Yunhe, what have you discovered?

16
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:11,080
I think there's nothing unusual.

17
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,980
One more lesson.

18
00:02:12,980 --> 00:02:19,200
When you judge a person, study not only his appearance but also what he wants to hide.

19
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:22,510
Li Shu.

20
00:02:26,940 --> 00:02:29,260
Wisteria tree?

21
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,560
What are you doing?

22
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:34,380
Sanyue, what day is it today?

23
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:36,120
The 5th day of the month.

24
00:02:36,987 --> 00:02:39,140
Going outside at night is not allowed.

25
00:02:39,140 --> 00:02:40,522
Go back.

26
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,340
Well, punish me.

27
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:48,960
In fact, I should punish you.

28
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:52,320
On the same day three years ago, I met you. Did you forget?

29
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:55,240
I should give you a gift today.

30
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:30,400
There was also a Wisteria tree where we first met.

31
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:35,300
When I found it in the valley, I wanted to give you a surprise.

32
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,280
It's also unsuitable.

33
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:00,580
If someone discovers, you'll be in trouble.

34
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:06,380
It was you who was the most unruly and fell in love with me.

35
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:09,400
Don't worry. It's just the two of us tonight.

36
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,430
Just tell me...

37
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:21,940
...if you like my gift.

38
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:29,420
How will you repay me?

39
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,849
What are they doing?

40
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,250
I...

41
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:12,040
Is that true?

42
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:14,880
Li Shu was nibbling Xue Sanyue's lips.

43
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:17,480
Xue Sanyue is usually indifferent.

44
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:23,260
But she's no different from any other in terms of love.

45
00:05:23,260 --> 00:05:24,780
How dare they?

46
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:27,200
Once Zhuyan seduced Earth Immortals into rebellion.

47
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:30,160
After it was suppressed, the control over Earth Immortals was strengthened.

48
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:33,060
Especially in Thousand Flower Valley in charge of training and defense.

49
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:38,120
To avoid favoritism due to affection, Spiritual Masters mustn't fall in love with Earth Immortals.

50
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:40,440
Shall we report them?

51
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:46,440
In Thousand Flower Valley, no one can survive without support.

52
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:49,100
We should make friends with them.

53
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,907
Master.

54
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:02,180
- Commander Xue.
- I've sealed off this place.

55
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:03,760
There is no entry.

56
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:05,440
Guardian Ji, go back.

57
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:09,900
I'm here not to see the merman, but you.

58
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:13,120
Guardian Ji, we don't seem to have any special friendship.

59
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:19,040
Yesterday, I saw something under the Wisteria tree.

60
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,480
Take it easy, Xue.

61
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:24,180
If I wanted to make trouble, I wouldn't have come to see you.

62
00:06:24,180 --> 00:06:27,000
I would have told Master Qingshu directly.

63
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,640
What do you want?

64
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,840
Cooperation.

65
00:06:33,840 --> 00:06:36,960
You're courageous and abide by morality.

66
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:38,600
Me, too.

67
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:43,120
Since we're the same, why not help each other?

68
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:46,300
You're good at judging others' inner thoughts.

69
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:51,080
But you fail to find that I hate being threatened.

70
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:55,000
Since you saw that, I must kill you.

71
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:16,869
Come with me! Let's go!

72
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,240
Sanyue, pay attention to the merman.

73
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,900
He was caught by Ji Yunhe.

74
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:28,646
He won't fight.

75
00:07:28,646 --> 00:07:32,032
Li Shu, keep away.

76
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:36,220
It's my turn.

77
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,680
Don't hurt her!

78
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:49,200
A merman speaks because of you?

79
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:51,300
What happened?

80
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:53,760
<i>Young Master,</i>

81
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:56,880
<i>someone saw Ji Yunhe and Xue Sanyue enter the Reflect Cave.</i>

82
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:59,180
<i>I'm afraid there's something unusual.</i>

83
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:06,420
They're coming!

84
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:08,380
Big trouble is coming.

85
00:08:08,380 --> 00:08:09,920
Lin Haoqing heard some news.

86
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,380
He's coming from there with a group of people.

87
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,980
Endless trouble today.

88
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:21,200
Li Shu, those three must die today.

89
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,226
You!

90
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:35,560
Why are you so naive? Why not make peace?

91
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:37,120
It's not easy.

92
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,460
I want to but...

93
00:08:38,460 --> 00:08:41,420
Commander Xue, could you calm down and talk with me?

94
00:08:41,420 --> 00:08:43,719
It's meaningless.

